SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT CMON_YEAR, cast (sum(CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESMAN + CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESAUTO) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTADEDUCTCRALLDISC) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTADEDUCTCRNOTALLDISC) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTADEDUCTCROTHER) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTNCREDNOTESNEWMAN + CMON_TOTNCREDNOTESNEWAUTO) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTNDEDUCTCRALLDISC) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTNDEDUCTCRNOTALLDISC) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum(CMON_TOTNDEDUCTCROTHER) as decimal (13,2)) FROM :1 where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR between :4 and :5 and CMON_MONTH between :6 and :7 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':8' group by CMON_YEAR for fetch only optimize for 100 rows
